snippet.title: Amiga Longplay: Skate Tribe [RE-PLAY]
snippet.description:
Originally a Atari ST game. Ported to the Amiga in AMOS. Have no idea if the Atari version has the the same low frame rate as the Amiga version.

Recorded this in 2012. Now replayed and improved 2018.

http://hol.abime.net/6279
